                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 11 月 30 日消息，AOC&nbsp;现已在京东上架一款型号为“Q27G41E”的&nbsp;27&nbsp;英寸显示器，这款显示器主打“2K 180Hz”，<strong>定价为&nbsp;849&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1180" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/20ae15ac-ebc1-4741-bc53-db3b90893867.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExMi5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="AOC 推出“Q27G41E”27 英寸显示器：2K 180Hz，849 元" width="730" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1178" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/4106a71f-bb63-45f0-93b8-ecffee43fc41.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC 推出“Q27G41E”27 英寸显示器：2K 180Hz，849 元" width="712" /></p><p>IT之家获悉，这款显示器配备&nbsp;2560x1440&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;180Hz Fast IPS&nbsp;面板，亮度&nbsp;300&nbsp;尼特，静态对比度&nbsp;1000:1，响应速度&nbsp;1ms，支持&nbsp;8-Bit&nbsp;色彩，覆盖&nbsp;93% DCI-P3&nbsp;色域。</p><p>这款显示器支架支持倾斜，显示器本体支持&nbsp;VESA 100x100mm&nbsp;壁挂，提供&nbsp;1&nbsp;个 HDMI 2.0&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;DP 1.4&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;3.5mm&nbsp;音频接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="658" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/6b7b7c5d-bdb6-4d61-b3eb-8ce69b48eb83.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC 推出“Q27G41E”27 英寸显示器：2K 180Hz，849 元" width="662" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/i1xTYRa" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/134541/9/47600/15735/673d9b7bF3fb8dd15/3008a72cf43fc3fd.jpg" title="AOC 推出“Q27G41E”27 英寸显示器：2K 180Hz，849 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> AOC“Q27G41E”27 英寸显示器</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 849 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明